{{wikipedia|Antifreeze}}
===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# A [[substance]], such as [[glycol]], used to lower the [[freezing point]] of [[water]]; used as an [[additive]] in the [[radiator]]s of [[motorcar]]s.

====Usage note====
*The plural form '''[[antifreezes]]''' is used only if more than one kind of antifreeze is meant.

